mic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/26619/', '', 'Pemetrexed, Cladribine, Trifluridine, Floxuridine, Nelarabine, Cytarabine, Pralatrexate, Decitabine, Azacitidine', 'Amlodipine, Valsartan, Acetylsalicylic acid, Ezetimibe, Bempedoic acid, Indapamide, Gemfibrozil, Evinacumab, Evolocumab, Probucol, Dextrothyroxine, More', 1767369485);
