ination with other agents that are potentially hepatotoxic (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/26630/', '', 'Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Tenofovir alafenamide, Maraviroc, Amprenavir, Simeprevir, Zanamivir, Cabotegravir, Lenacapavir, Telaprevir, Velpatasvir, More', 'Bempedoic acid, Evinacumab, Evolocumab, Dextrothyroxine, Cholestyramine, Clofibrate, Colestipol, Bempedoic acid, Colesevelam, Alirocumab', 1767369485);
